title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync
description: The JarExporter is causing an out of sync issue.
OB: The exported jar file includes itself when it shouldn't.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported jar in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported jar file the second time.

Note: This issue occurs when overwriting the exported jar file in the same directory.
